org.wildfly.swarm.config.messaging.activemq.server

Class CoreAddress<T extends CoreAddress<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.HashMap
        • org.wildfly.swarm.config.messaging.activemq.server.CoreAddress<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map

    public class CoreAddress<T extends CoreAddress<T>>
extends HashMap
    A runtime-only resource representing a ActiveMQ "address". Zero or more queues can be bound to a single address. When a message is routed, it is routed to the set of queues bound to the message's address.
    See Also:
